snippet.title: Paper Wars: Cannon Fodder Devastated - Nintendo Switch Announcement Trailer - Europe
snippet.description: Paper Wars: Cannon Fodder Devastated is coming to Nintendo Switch in Europe, North America, Australia, New Zealand and South Africa on the March 1st!
